The repository contains the following first-party workspace crates under the
same MIT OR Apache-2.0 license expression:

- cobol_packed
- cobol-codegen-rust
- cobol-dialect
- cobol-ir
- cobol-platform
- cobol-record
- cobol-runtime
- cobol-sema
- cobol-source
- cobol-syntax
- cobol-text
- cobol-vm

GnuCOBOL is used only as an external oracle test executable when the
oracle_gnucobol test suite is run. It is not linked into the converter, not
vendored into this repository, and not bundled in release archives produced by
the standard release workflow.

Release packages include a Cargo metadata SBOM so downstream redistributors can
review exact dependency versions and declared license expressions for the build.
